item.description:
Development Some notes to remember when working from source&hellip;
Commits Before committing, run the bin/pre-commit script to&hellip;
 regenerate fakes go fmt source files run all tests build all binaries regenerate client command docs  Review for unexpected changes before including them in your commit.
Shortcuts Some shortcuts instead of the built-in go commands&hellip;
go run  bin/ssoca-client &ndash; shortcut to run the client from source in any directory bin/ssoca-server &ndash; shortcut to run the server from source in any directory  go build Run bin/build to build both client and server for all supported architectures and operating systems.
